  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div xml:id="KT12-kilavi">
          <p type="edition">āṟṟāḷ eṉak kavaṉṟa tōḻikkuk kiḻatti uraittatu.</p>
          <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Spoken by HER to the confidante who was anxious that she might not have the strength in the time of separation.</p>
          </div>

        <div xml:id="KT12">
            <lg type="edition">
<l>                eṟumpi yaḷaiyiṟ kuṟumpal cuṉaiya</l>
<l>                vulaikka laṉṉa pāṟai yēṟik</l>
<l>                koṭuvi leyiṉar pakaḻi māykkuṅ</l>
<l>                kavalait teṉpavavar tērceṉṟa vāṟē</l>
<l>                yatumaṟ ṟavalaṅ koḷḷātu</l>
<l>                notumaṟ kaḻaṟumiv vaḻuṅka lūrē.</l>
            </lg>
        
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>The way his chariot has gone, they say, has crossroads</l>
<l rend="indent">where hunters with bent bows sharpen arrows,</l>
<l rend="indent">climbing on rocks [hot] as the stone of a smithy</l>
<l rend="indent2">with many pools tiny as ant holes.</l>
<l rend="indent">Without taking in just that is troubling,</l>
    

        
      </lg>
        </div>
